175 sqq. Erigone: all the tropic signs save Libra are preceded by a binum signum ; Cancer by Gemini, Capricorn by Sagittarius, Aries by Pisces. Accordingly, lest any tropic sign should not be pre- ceded by a binum signum, Virgo, who precedes Libra, binis numeratur in astris, is counted as a binum signum.
